# Codefinity SQL Practice

![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-work%20in%20progress-yellow)

This folder contains my SQL exercises completed during my Codefinity learning journey.

I use this space to organize my course-based SQL practice and track my progress step by step.

## What I practice here

* Basic SQL queries
* `SELECT` statements
* Filtering data with `WHERE`
* Sorting results with `ORDER BY`
* Working with tables
* Simple database exercises

## Purpose

The goal of this folder is to document my SQL learning progress and keep all Codefinity-related exercises in one place.

This is part of my broader learning path toward QA, databases, and technical skills development.

